    <h1>Feminism</h1>
    <hr style="width:100%;">
    <p>Feminism is the belief that women should have the same rights, power, and opportunities as men, 
        and be treated in the same way. It can also refer to the organized activities that support women's 
        rights and interests. </p>
        <hr>
        <p>Some examples of feminist goals include: 
        Equal pay in the workplace
        Reproductive rights
        Women's suffrage
        The right to an education
        Fighting against gender stereotypes
        Protection against sexual harassment and assault
        The right to own property</p>


    
